content: Hi - thanks so much! Have you taken a training with us yet?
Yes, I have.  I keep checking to begin.  So, am I missing something?

Thanks! Nope - you're okay (I see you form/quiz in our sheet). We are still working through everyone who did the Wednesday night training. So you should receive a Direct Message from one of our moderators by later today. To check Direct Messages, it's the top left of Discord
In the meantime -- please update your Discord Display Name to a first and last name. To do this, click on "User Settings" (gear icon on the bottom) left and Edit Profile

thank you for your response.  I am worried about my name being shown on any texts I do, it's unusual and easy to track.  That's why I shortened it to "Dab".  Will my name appear on texts?  That doesn't work for me.
When I texted in 2022, I used a different name -- please help me with this issue.

Understood! That's fine -- if you prefer to use Dab as your first name in texting, just keep is as Dab here (but you do need to update your profile to have a full last name -- last names won't show on texts)
